        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-base font-medium text-gray-500">
          Integrating with existing systems is smooth and hassle-free, thanks to
          our incredible flexible approach. Equipped with advanced features and
          tools, our solution effortlessly manages complex tasks and workflows.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-12">
          <button
            class="flex items-center justify-center h-10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-200 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 hover:to-indigo-800 shadow focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-950 focus:ring-offset-2 ring-offset-gray-200 hover:shadow-none"
            aria-label="Action">
            Get started
          </button>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
            <span class="block">This is some support text</span>
            <span class="block">and this is also.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="mx-auto grid mt-10 grid-cols-4 items-center gap-x-8 gap-y-10 sm:grid-cols-4 sm:gap-x-10  ">
          {
            logos.map((logo) => (
              <img
                class={`${logo.colSpan} max-h-12 w-full object-contain `}
                src={logo.src}
                alt="#_"
                width={logo.width}
                height={logo.height}
              />
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="relative lg:col-span-5 lg:-mr-8 xl:absolute xl:inset-0 xl:left-1/2 xl:mr-0 lg:border-l">
      <img
        class="aspect-[3/2] w-full bg-gray-50 object-cover lg:absolute lg:inset-0 lg:aspect-auto lg:h-full"
